snippet.title: Tarisland Worldview Trailer
snippet.description:
A new world awaits. As frost's grip wanes, chill whispers begin.
Follow our steps to reveal the story of Tarisland!
▶ Sign-up on http://tarisglobal.com/
▶ Discord: https://discord.com/invite/bTW9VHehCk

Our first closed beta test is coming soon.
You can also find us on...
▶ Twitter: https://twitter.com/Taris_Official
▶ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Tarislandofficial
